\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {5.2}{\ignorespaces Decomposition of the \SI {1.08}{\second } gap between the simulated \SI {75}{\metre } time and the analytical lower bound of Eq.~\ref {eq:analytical_bound}. Each row converts an energy-loss channel, integrated over the run, into an equivalent time penalty against the \SI {80}{\kilo \watt } reference. The traction-limited deficit integrates the shortfall $P_\text  {max} - P_\text  {elec}(t)$ over the launch phase; the residual absorbs the overlap between channels and the \SI {80}{\milli \second } launch-torque ramp.}}{67}{table.caption.58}\protected@file@percent }
